description.en:
Captain token is the main token and store of value for CaptainSwap and will also be used to create value for CaptainSwap's utility token $CREW. $CREW will be tethered to the price of $CAPT which in turn adds incentive for people to HODL $CAPT

Captain token was started by our Captain, Capt. George. Capt. was tired of rugrulls on the BSC so he set out to create a token that his crew could trust...
